{"tid":682646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12連熱　體感溫度最高達46.7℃","createTime":"2018-05-29T04:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T02:41:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"06288486834ca9391138d049638d9164c652c4c7","tid":682646,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:40:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180529/20404659\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F20404659&d=MFJqdupFcKWnelv73%2FLeok4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=45acdb80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180529%2F20404659&h=cd76c84e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180529/20404659</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月29日 <br />\n<br />\n12連熱　體感溫度最高達46.7℃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180529/large/a0702a1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180529%2Flarge%2Fa0702a1.gif&h=33713e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■天文台昨日錄得市區最高氣溫為34.5℃。黎樹雄攝 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港連續第12日氣溫升至33℃或以上，天文台錄得市區最高氣溫34.5℃，繼續打破天文台自1884年以來5月份最長酷熱天氣紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市區最高氣溫約34.5℃<br />\n<br />\n有民間氣象組織推算，體感溫度在靠近中午時份最高，橫瀾島錄得整日最高達46.7℃。天文台預料今日天氣酷熱，市區最高氣溫約34.5℃，隨後兩、三日持續酷熱。<br />\n<br />\n民間氣象組織「地下天文台」根據天文台公佈的氣溫及濕度，推算體感溫度，發現部份地區「酷熱指數」超過40℃。全日錄得最熱一刻為早上11時40分，橫瀾島體感溫度高達46.7℃，而同一時間長洲亦錄得43.9℃，市區則錄得39.7℃酷熱指數。<br />\n<br />\n天文台亦有公佈類似體感氣溫的「暑熱指數」，市區京士柏氣象站及雙魚河氣象站暑熱指數分別逼近30和29，較前日稍降1度。<br />\n至於為何錄得的氣溫與體感溫度有差別，翻查資料，「地下天文台」曾發表網誌解釋，認為氣溫不能完全反映體感溫度，指出濕度、風勢和日照時間，都會影響人體對酷熱的感覺，當濕度高時，皮膚上的水份較難蒸發，便會感覺較悶熱。<br />\n<br />\n天文台台長岑智明曾指，體感溫度沒有統一標準，故天文台未有跟隨美國氣象部門的方程式，而是在市區的京士柏和郊區的雙魚河氣象站，另設獨立儀器，測量濕球、黑球和乾球溫度，經自家研發的方程式，計算「暑熱指數」，天文台會參考指數發出酷熱警告，如指數達30屬炎熱，會提醒市民小心中暑。<br />\n<br />\n■記者梁銘恩  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n存水量比去年同期跌10百分點　 多處乾塘　十萬水急<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n救生員不足　公共泳池頻封閉"},{"pid":"5e5be3fa6375c63235026db51278884650b4eb36","tid":682646,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:48:40.000Z","msg":"行一步已經濕撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df6a211616e1ba1f579eb11e30184dd6eabe91f","tid":682646,"uid":26156,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:49:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bcd0ffe8b2372c2d2cb644f2712eddbcf16ecb4","tid":682646,"uid":30578,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:50:59.000Z","msg":"次次都影女<br />\n搵次影仔得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n濕鳩報紙佬"},{"pid":"66d7ff56d163530daa712fad01e616bc6990b4da","tid":682646,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e5be3fa6375c63235026db51278884650b4eb36","tid":682646,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:48:40.000Z","msg":"行一步已經濕撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:51:49.000Z","msg":"我係屋企行十分鐘去巴士站已經滴晒汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193e9a35f99987ffc0b31e01db3d2f2a783909cf","tid":682646,"uid":28743,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0df6a211616e1ba1f579eb11e30184dd6eabe91f","tid":682646,"uid":26156,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:49:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:52:32.000Z","msg":"仲有半年先出返黎 慢慢等啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c0624317227b81a3987fc367e41e16683e96f3a","tid":682646,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T04:52:54.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係著西裝返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都要著長褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/d